C4AUD.original: ~z~Me done wit dat blood clot suit, ya know Niko.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~我再也不跟那个混蛋合作了，Niko。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yo Niko, got some serious fire power up in here. Rocket launcher! Bo!
C4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，Niko，这边有个真家伙。火箭发射器！嘭！

C4AUD.original: ~z~Chill Niko, we catch him soon enough.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Chill Niko, we catch him soon enough.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Take him inna Middle Park. Dere ain't too many people over dere.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Take him inna Middle Park. Dere ain't too many people over dere.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Now it is our turn to get him to help us.
~z~Rhaatid, Niko. I don't got no shot no more.
~z~Yo Respect! Ya a rightous rudeboy, Niko
~z~Get up, Niko, get up. Give me some height.
~z~Steady now man, me need fe shoot!
~z~Let's find him and get this over with. I don't like being in this man's pocket.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~赶紧找着目标结束战斗吧。我不喜欢被这人使唤。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I do not think he can ask us to do more than this.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~这已经是他能要求我们做的最后一件事了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Give the tourists something to tell their families back home.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Give the tourists something to tell their families back home.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, but me done wit dis ting ya know, Niko.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~确实，但我和这事就此两清了，Niko。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Girl wine up and ting, like she looking for something and ting
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Girl wine up and ting, like she looking for something and ting

C4AUD.original: ~z~Cha, what you doing? Me had him in me sight!
~z~There be the other chopper. Stick to him, Niko. We need to take him down where there be no people.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~目标在那里。跟住他，Niko。~n~要到无人区才能把他打下来。

C4AUD.original: ~z~We need fe get higher so me can get dis shot.
~z~Jacob, how'd they get you into this shit?
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob, how'd they get you into this shit?

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yo, job well done ya know Niko, but we haffi get out dis bumba clot debt right now, ya know.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，干得漂亮，Niko。~n~不过我们还是得把这逼的人情债给解决掉。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I have a feeling that it was best to do what we did though.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~不过我觉得今天的活最好还是得干。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I thought de girl was too good to be true ya know Niko.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~I thought de girl was too good to be true ya know Niko.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Jacob. You really gotta smoke that thing now?
C4AUD.translated: ~z~我靠，Jacob。你非得现在抽那玩意吗？

C4AUD.original: ~z~For real. I'm gwan give dem boy some hot fe jump for!
C4AUD.translated: ~z~For real. I'm gwan give dem boy some hot fe jump for!

C4AUD.original: ~z~We shot down that chopper for you.
~z~Yo Respect! Ya a rightous rudeboy, Niko
C4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，敬你！你真是个给力的莽娃，Niko。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Me no go back inna no more blood clot helicopter wit di boy ya know, no more!
C4AUD.translated: ~z~我不会再替这种人上什么狗屁直升机了，再也不会了！

C4AUD.original: ~z~Some bigga ess put some pressure pon me and call me up in him office and tell me all type of nonsense.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Some bigga ess put some pressure pon me and call me up in him office and tell me all type of nonsense.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Ya going through the arch? Ya crazy? Don't get me killed!
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Ya going through the arch? Ya crazy? Don't get me killed!

C4AUD.original: ~z~Get dis ting up higher so me can shoot dis ras clot.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~把飞机往高拉，否则打不到他。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Come on, Jacob. You need new lenses in those glasses? Hit the thing.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~拜托，Jacob。你的眼镜度数不够了吗？打准点。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Don't go hitting a crane or nothing.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Don't go hitting a crane or nothing.

C4AUD.original: ~z~and tell me some I haffi come up here and meet him, and den find some boy and mash him up and ting.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~and tell me some I haffi come up here and meet him, and den find some boy and mash him up and ting.

C4AUD.original: ~z~I can't take a shot with dis damn turbulence ting going on.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~你一直乱动，根本没法好好打。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yeah! Only we could get arrested or killed.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~对！但我们有可能被捕甚至遇难。

C4AUD.original: ~z~You gotta work on your aim, Jacob. I could have made that shot with my eyes closed.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~多练练瞄准吧，Jacob。我闭着眼睛都能打着他。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I am sorry for getting you into this. It was that girl, Michelle. She played me.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~I am sorry for getting you into this. It was that girl, Michelle. She played me.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Dammit. Maybe he should have been taken down anyway.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~妈的。说不定该不惜一切代价击落他。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Make we dweet. Get the chopper in place.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Make we dweet. Get the chopper in place.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Ya man, It just some almshouse gwaan ya know. Forward a chopper, see America? It's a real fucked up place man.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Ya man, It just some almshouse gwaan ya know. Forward a chopper, see America? It's a real fucked up place man.

C4AUD.original: ~z~He was last spotted in Varsity Heights. No civilian casualties.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~最后一次目击他是在Varsity Heights。~n~避免平民伤亡。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Shows you the people who need spy shit done get other people to do their dirty work.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~结论是，需要特务行动的人~n~会找别人做这种脏活。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Not a bad way to die. I'll be in touch.
~z~I need fe take a shot soon, sight?
C4AUD.translated: ~z~I need fe take a shot soon, sight?

C4AUD.original: ~z~Cha, missed the ras clot. Get me back in I spot.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~操，没打中那狗逼。再让它进入射程。

C4AUD.original: ~z~We had a few chopper troubles. This isn't going to be possible.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~出了点直升机事故，任务无法执行了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Get close so I can take a shot!
~z~How am I gonna get dis bumba clot with ya moving all over de place?
C4AUD.translated: ~z~你丫一直晃悠我怎么可能打着他？

C4AUD.original: ~z~I an' I be too high fe get de shot, Niko.
~z~He's over the water. Now are the time.
~z~Yo, I an' I see ya soon Niko.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Yo, I an' I see ya soon Niko.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Can't shoot dis bumba clot from back here.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Can't shoot dis bumba clot from back here.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Why'd you miss, Jacob? Smoking too much?
~z~Ya man, It just some almshouse gwaan ya know. Forward a chopper, see America? It's a real fucked up place man.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Ya man, It just some almshouse gwaan ya know. Forward a chopper, see America? It's a real fucked up place man.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Niko, I needed you to come through on this. I'll be in touch.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我需要你成功完成任务。保持联络。

C4AUD.original: ~z~and tell me some I haffi come up here and meet him, and den find some boy and mash him up and ting.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~and tell me some I haffi come up here and meet him, and den find some boy and mash him up and ting.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Ras. De chopper ain't in good shape and ting. It fuckery to the fullness, seen?
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Ras. De chopper ain't in good shape and ting. It fuckery to the fullness, seen?

C4AUD.original: ~z~Cha, me no come yah fe hear bout how horse dead and cow fat. It nuh nuttin.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Cha, me no come yah fe hear bout how horse dead and cow fat. It nuh nuttin.

C4AUD.original: ~z~He paid his debt to our country. He did a good thing. Maybe that was the one good thing he did.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~他为国捐躯了，做了件好事。也许这是他做的唯一一件好事。

C4AUD.original: ~z~De boss gonna be vex with I an' I for losing dat ras clot ya know, cha!
C4AUD.translated: ~z~跟丢了那个狗逼，雇主会很生气的，操！

C4AUD.original: ~z~Bellic. We need you. Now. The chopper is prepped and waiting off Grummer Road in Northwood.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Bellic，我们需要你。立刻。直升机已经准备好了，在Northwood的Grummer路待命。

C4AUD.original: ~z~He wasn't my man, he was your target. Lives may be lost because of this mistake.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~他不是我的人，是你的目标。你的失误可能会害死人。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I will try to find the man you're after. I will call when I have something.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~我会尽力寻找你要的人的。有消息了就联系你。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Dis some real spy shit I and I is doing ya know.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~咱俩现在这是真正的特务行动。

C4AUD.original: ~z~It's like we in a movie or something.
~z~Rhaatid. Him back over on land again.
~z~Your sometime accomplice, Jacob, is there. He's riding shotgun on this one.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~你之前的帮凶Jacob也在。这次他负责火力支援。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I appreciate your assistance, Bellic. You did a good thing today. Now it's my turn.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~很感谢你的协助，Bellic。~n~今天你做了件好事。现在轮到我了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Gwann chill out Niko, we jammin' here.
~z~Come down, Niko. I an' I need fe get lower for de shot and ting.
~z~It isn't easy to follow orders when you don't know what the fuck is going on.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~服从那些你都不知道在搞毛的命令是不容易。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Seen. He got that government ting about him. All for the greater good and ting.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~懂。他上头还有政府啥的在。都是为大局着想。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Hey, me and Jacob kind of messed up.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Hey, me and Jacob kind of messed up.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Him going through City Hall. That's a seriously tight fit.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Him going through City Hall. That's a seriously tight fit.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Ya got some crucial flying skills, ya know Niko. Can I drop I off on de heli pad though? Me no feel so good ya know.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~你的飞行技术真不错，Niko。~n~能不能把我送到停机坪？我现在感觉不太好。

C4AUD.original: ~z~We lost Jacob in this piece of shit mission of yours.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~就因为你的狗屁任务，Jacob他没了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yo, dis be some crazy shit ya know Niko. Yo, we inna the Star Junction in a helicopter.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，这可太疯狂了，Niko。~n~开着直升机在星汇广场里边转悠。

C4AUD.original: ~z~For a man who has asked me to kill a lot of men, this guy is really safety conscious.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~虽然这家伙让我杀了很多人，~n~但他真的很重视安全。

C4AUD.original: ~z~We had to shoot the chopper down over land.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~We had to shoot the chopper down over land.

C4AUD.original: ~z~And I'm paranoid enough with US government on my ass.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~光是被美国政府胁迫就让我有够偏执了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Maybe the casualties would have been fewer overall.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~说不定平民伤亡也没那么多。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Don't ask unnecessary questions. I want you to take out this guy's chopper.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~别问多余的问题。你需要击落某人的直升机。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Good place to hide if the government are after you.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Good place to hide if the government are after you.

C4AUD.original: ~z~I tink dat's our boy over der ya know. Get him so we can go home man.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~I tink dat's our boy over der ya know. Get him so we can go home man.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Some bigga ess put some pressure pon me and call me up in him office and tell me all type of nonsense.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Some bigga ess put some pressure pon me and call me up in him office and tell me all type of nonsense.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Trust me, dis ting a mess wit me structure.
~z~Yo, bring dis ting down me breda. I can't get him from up here.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，飞低点，我的兄弟。这么高我打不到他。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Wicked Niko, ya don't know, ya de man, ya know? Sight de man soon, seen?
~z~The secondary smoke doesn't exactly help my hand-eye coordination.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~二手烟只会给我的手眼协调帮倒忙。

C4AUD.original: ~z~He trying to lose I and I through City Hall.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~He trying to lose I and I through City Hall.

C4AUD.original: ~z~Fuck the math. This is no way to fight a war. There might be another opportunity.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~去他妈的算术。仗不是这么打的。会有下次机会的。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yo just chill Niko, you can always head around.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Yo just chill Niko, you can always head around.

C4AUD.original: ~z~I have the feeling he don't want to be responsible for a helicopter crash in Middle Park.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~感觉他是不想为~n~中心公园的坠机事故负责。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, how'd they get you into this shit?
C4AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob, how'd they get you into this shit?

C4AUD.original: ~z~Ya make me lose de shot ya know man!
~z~I'd be impressed if you had been.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~真这样的话我会印象深刻的。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I don't see so good when you're blowing the smoke in my face!
C4AUD.translated: ~z~你对着我的脸吞云吐雾会挡视线的！

C4AUD.original: ~z~Yo, I ain't used to seeing de Star Junction from a helicopter, ya know Niko.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~哟，从直升机上看星汇广场还真不习惯，Niko。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Mek we get lower, bredren. There be no shot up here.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~飞低一点，兄弟。这么高打不了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Rhaatid, that just fuckery. I need to be back inna line.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，吃狗屎吧。保持同一高度。

C4AUD.original: ~z~What do you mean? Is full of rich joggers and tourists.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~What do you mean? Is full of rich joggers and tourists.

C4AUD.original: ~z~We couldn't get a clean shot on the chopper.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~我们没法安全击落那架直升机了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~I don't care what type of prison sentence de boy want check me with, ya know star. No more ah dis.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~我才不管他想判我几年，兄弟。我是受不了了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~Raas Man!, I get no more shot!
~z~Give me some height some can shoot dis ras clot and ting, Niko.
~z~If someone can find the man I search for, it should be him.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~如果说还有谁能找到我要的人，那就是他了。

C4AUD.original: ~z~You think I've been sitting around scratching my balls with my head up my ass.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~你以为我是一直坐着低头挠蛋吗？

C4AUD.original: ~z~Don't worry about the bridge, Jacob. I'm finally getting the hang of flying this thing.
C4AUD.translated: ~z~不用担心撞桥，Jacob。~n~我已经掌握开这玩意的诀窍了。
